    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use the <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/List.html#toArray%28T%5B%5D%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>toArray(T[] arr)</code></a> method.</p>\n<pre><code>.getMap(locations.toArray(new WorldLocation[0]))\n</code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p>Here's a complete example:</p>\n<pre><code>public static void method(String... strs) {\n    for (String s : strs)\n        System.out.println(s);\n}\n\n...\n    List&lt;String&gt; strs = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\n    strs.add(&quot;hello&quot;);\n    strs.add(&quot;world&quot;);\n    \n    method(strs.toArray(new String[0]));\n    //     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n...\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
